  fb:m.02896 fb:sports.sports_team.colors ?color .
  ?color rdfs:label ?color_label .
  FILTER ( lang( ?color_label ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?institution_name WHERE {
  fb:m.019fz fb:people.person.education ?education_entity .
  ?education_entity fb:education.education.institution ?institution .
  ?institution rdfs:label ?institution_name
  FILTER ( lang( ?institution_name ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?spouse ?spouse_name WHERE {
  fb:m.05np4c fb:people.person.spouse_s ?marriage .
  ?marriage fb:people.marriage.spouse ?spouse .
  ?spouse rdfs:label ?spouse_name .
  FILTER ( lang( ?spouse_name ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?wife ?startDate WHERE {
  fb:m.03p77 fb:people.person.spouse_s ?marriage .
  ?marriage fb:people.marriage.spouse ?spouse .
  ?marriage fb:people.marriage.from ?startDate .
  FILTER ( ?spouse != fb:m.03p77 ) ?spouse rdfs:label ?wifeLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?wifeLabel ) = 'en' ) BIND( STR( ?wifeLabel ) AS ?wife )
}
ORDER BY ?startDate
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?date WHERE {
  fb:m.0713r fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship fb:time.event.start_date ?date .
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?date )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>

  fb:m.02d9k fb:sports.pro_athlete.sports_played_professionally ?playedSportInstance .
  ?playedSportInstance fb:sports.pro_sports_played.sport ?sport .
  ?sport rdfs:label ?sportLabel .

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?team ?team_name WHERE {
  fb:m.0839s fb:sports.pro_athlete.teams ?roster .
  ?roster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.team ?team .
  ?roster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.from ?start_year .
  ?team fb:type.object.name ?team_name .
  FILTER ( lang( ?team_name ) = "en" )
}
ORDER BY ?start_year
LIMIT 1
